org.cyclops.cyclopscore.tracking

Class Versions

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cyclops.cyclopscore.tracking.Versions

  • public class Versions
extends java.lang.Object
    Version checking service. This will check for a regular text file at the given url for each mod. This file must conform to the following format: [version] [version info] [update url]
